{"id":147857,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/04/切尔诺贝利核事故25周年/","date":"2011-04-26T10:00:25Z","modified":"2011-04-26T10:00:25Z","title":"切尔诺贝利核事故25周年","content":"<div>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">波恩</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">切尔诺贝利核电站事故发生</span><span>25</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">周年纪念日之际，全球各地今天（</span><span>4</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">月</span><span>25</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">日）举行各种活动，纪念人类有史以来迄今最大的核电事故。切尔诺贝利核电站所在国家乌克兰首都基辅敲响</span><span>25</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">次钟声，俄罗斯东正教大主教基里尔（</span><span>Patirarch Kirill</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）在追思弥撒中指出，这个世界还从未在和平时期经历过可以与切尔诺贝利核事故相比较的灾难。</span><span>1986</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年</span><span>4</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">月</span><span>26</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">日，切尔诺贝利核电站</span><span>4</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">号反应堆发生爆炸，释放出大量可导致癌症的发射性微粒，使欧洲广大地区受到影响，数十万人不得不离开家乡。受灾最重的前苏维埃共和国乌克兰和俄罗斯两国的总统今天前往以切尔诺贝利核电站为中心的禁区，参加纪念活动。</span> <span lang=\"ZH-CN\">根据不同的估计，切尔诺贝利核电事故导致</span><span>1</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">万至</span><span>10</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">万以上人丧生。当年紧急浇筑的反应堆混凝土罩壳多年来随时可能坍塌，急需被新的保护罩所替代，新保护罩工程将耗资</span><span>16</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">亿欧元。</span></p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGltcHJlc3Npb24iLCAicHJvcGVydGllcyI6IHsidG9rZW4iOiAiYTRhNDYwYTM5MDRlZWU4ZmY1ZTAyNGVhNGJkZTdhYzIifX0=&#038;ip=1&#038;img=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" /><img src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /><a href=\"http://fulltextrssfeed.com\"><img src=\"http://fulltextrssfeed.com/images/1x1.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"ftrf - full text rss\" /></a><a href=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGNsaWNrIiwgInByb3BlcnRpZXMiOiB7InRva2VuIjogImE0YTQ2MGEzOTA0ZWVlOGZmNWUwMjRlYTRiZGU3YWMyIn19&#038;ip=1&#038;redirect=http://talkita.com/wrap?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw-world.de%2Fdw%2Farticle%2F0%2C%2C15029706%2C00.html%3Fmaca%3Dchi-rss-chi-all-1127-rdf&#038;title=%E5%88%87%E5%B0%94%E8%AF%BA%E8%B4%9D%E5%88%A9%E6%A0%B8%E4%BA%8B%E6%95%8525%E5%91%A8%E5%B9%B4\">Chat about this story w/ Talkita</a></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":176,"categories":[8779],"tags":[15660]}